  "title": "Garlicky Canadian Seafood Chowder",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful keto-friendly chowder featuring a rich seafood stock, garlic, and a crunchy texture, perfect for a hangover cure. This Canadian-inspired dish is made with a variety of seafood and spices.",
